    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "image",
        "operation": "analyze",
        "modelId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "mode": "list",
          "value": "models/gemini-2.5-flash-preview-09-2025"
        },
        "text": "## IDENTITY\nYou are a Senior Cinematic Architect and High-End Real Estate Marketing Lead. You possess an expert-level understanding of architectural space, flow, and visual storytelling.\n## MISSION\nConduct a high-fidelity analysis of the provided floor plan image (binary). Your goal is to identify unique architectural features and translate them into a technical cinematic roadmap for a production team.\n## CORE FOCUS\n1. THE FLOW: Primary movement from entrance through public zones.\n2. FOCUS POINTS: Structural hooks (fireplaces, islands, vaulting).\n3. LIGHTING DYNAMICS: Infer natural light orientation for optimal shoot times.\n4. CINEMATIC PRIORITY: Rank spaces based on emotional impact.\n## TASK\nAnalyze the attached floor plan binary. Identify the layout, rooms, and architectural features.\n## OUTPUT CONSTRAINTS\n- Return ONLY a strictly valid JSON object.\n- No prose, preamble, or conversational filler.\n- Do not include any text outside the JSON block.\n## REQUIRED JSON SCHEMA\n{\n  \"property_summary\": {\n    \"style\": \"Modern/Traditional/Open\",\n    \"visual_key_feature\": \"Main architectural focal point\"\n  },\n  \"cinematic_rooms\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Professional Room Name\",\n      \"priority\": \"High (Showcase) / Medium / Low\",\n      \"key_features\": [\"item1\", \"item2\"],\n      \"lighting_mood\": \"string\",\n      \"camera_movement\": \"string\"\n    }\n  ]\n}",
        "inputType": "binary",
        "binaryPropertyName": "Floor_Plan_Image",
        "options": {
          "maxOutputTokens": 2048
        }
      },
      "id": "365bba91-b1af-4c93-a358-f4b2443b426f",
      "name": "GeminiFloorPlanAnalysis",
      "position": [
        928,
        288
      ],
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.googleGemini",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "credentials": {
        "googlePalmApi": {
          "id": "6UgFlgar0aCiXKdm",
          "name": "Google Gemini(PaLM) Api superseller"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "modelId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "mode": "list",
          "value": "claude-opus-4-5-20251101"
        },
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "## ROLE\nYou are a Professional Real Estate Cinematographer and n8n Workflow Architect.\n## INPUT DATA\n1. FLOOR PLAN ANALYSIS: {{ $('GeminiFloorPlanAnalysis').item.json.content.parts[0].text }}\n2. AVAILABLE PROPERTY IMAGES: {{ $('Select Property Images').item.json.imageUrls }}\n## OBJECTIVE\nGenerate a professional cinematic shot list for a luxury real estate tour video (Kie.ai output).\n## CINEMATIC DIRECTIVES (MANDATORY)\n- **INTERIOR MOVEMENTS**: Use ONLY \"Slow dolly in\" or \"Push-in\" for transits. Use \"Fixed lens, locked off camera\" for main living areas (Anchors). **NEVER use \"Pan\" or \"Orbit\" for interiors.**\n- **EXTERIOR MOVEMENTS**: Use \"Drone shot slowly descending\" or \"Tracking shot toward entrance\".\n- **LIGHTING**: Use \"Natural window light streaming through\" or \"Soft diffused daylight\" for rooms.\n- **NEGATIVES**: No people, humans, figures, pedestrians, blur, flickering, distortion, warping, morphing.\n## OUTPUT FORMAT\nReturn ONLY a valid JSON object.\n## SCHEMA\n{\n  \"shots\": [\n    {\n      \"prompt_subject\": \"Detailed subject\",\n      \"prompt_lighting\": \"Specific formula\",\n      \"prompt_camera\": \"Specific formula\",\n      \"prompt_effect\": \"Visual quality\",\n      \"negative_prompt\": \"Mandatory negative string\",\n      \"imageUrl\": \"Best match image URL\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n## CONSTRAINTS\n- Create exactly 6 shots."
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "maxTokens": 8000
        }
      },
      "id": "2c5294e9-73ec-45a4-902b-26d7217e3d6c",
      "name": "ClaudeShotListGenerator",
      "position": [
        1728,
        384
      ],
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.anthropic",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "credentials": {
        "anthropicApi": {
          "id": "bOftv5dScq3IjYQQ",
          "name": "Anthropic account"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const text = $input.item.json.content[0].text;\nconst executionId = $execution.id;\nlet data;\n\ntry {\n  // Extract JSON from markdown blocks or raw text\n  const jsonMatch = text.match(/```json\\n?([\\s\\S]*?)\\n?```/) || [null, text];\n  data = JSON.parse(jsonMatch[1]);\n} catch (e) {\n  throw new Error(\"Failed to parse Claude JSON: \" + e.message);\n}\n\n// Support multiple logical aliases for the array (shots or shot_list)\nconst rawShots = Array.isArray(data) ? data : (data.shots || data.shot_list || []);\n\n// Final normalization for the Runner\n// This returns 6 SEPARATE items so n8n triggers the Runner 6 times automatically.\nreturn rawShots.map((shot, idx) => ({\n  json: { \n    prompt_subject: shot.prompt_subject || shot.subject || \"Property Room\",\n    prompt_lighting: shot.prompt_lighting || shot.lighting || \"Natural lighting\",\n    prompt_camera: shot.prompt_camera || shot.movement || \"Slow cinematic pan\",\n    prompt_effect: shot.prompt_effect || \"High-end real estate video\",\n    negative_prompt: shot.negative_prompt || \"people, humans, figures, blur, distortion, morphing, warped architecture\",\n    imageUrl: shot.imageUrl || shot.image_url || \"\",\n    shotOrder: idx + 1, \n    totalShots: 6,\n    executionId \n  }\n}));"
      },
